  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para><list>
<item>Describe several different types of thermometers</item>
<item>Convert temperatures between the Celsius, Fahrenheit, and Kelvin scales</item>
</list></md:abstract>
  <md:language>en</md:language>
